abstract: The president’s re-election campaign may offer some surprises in its pitch to American voters.
snippet: The president’s re-election campaign may offer some surprises in its pitch to American voters.
lead_paragraph: Addressing his cheering supporters in New Hampshire, Bernie Sanders declared, “This victory here is the beginning of the end for Donald Trump.”

abstract: Across 60 nations, Trump supporters are outliers on their views on economic inequality. But their actions suggest it’s not a core philosophical difference.
snippet: Across 60 nations, Trump supporters are outliers on their views on economic inequality. But their actions suggest it’s not a core philosophical difference.
lead_paragraph: American conservatives are global outliers in views about the fairness of income inequality, and they’re among the most likely to attribute such inequality to merit, an ambitious global survey reveals.

abstract: A campaign of sponsored content for the candidate flourished suddenly on Instagram. A new outfit, called Meme 2020, is behind it.

abstract: Coronavirus, Pope Francis, Roger Stone: Here’s what you need to know.
snippet: Coronavirus, Pope Francis, Roger Stone: Here’s what you need to know.
lead_paragraph: Coronavirus cases had seemed to be leveling off, but then new numbers showed the largest one-day increase recorded so far. There were nearly 15,000 new cases in Hubei Province alone, with 242 additional deaths. A change in diagnostic criteria could be part of the reason. Here’s the latest.

abstract: Some of President Donald Trump’s top foreign policy priorities stand at pivotal moments as two high-level national security officials head to an annual security forum in Germany. Strains in the trans-Atlantic relationship have cast doubt on whether they can count on much help from European leaders in advancing Trump’s agenda.

lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Some of President Donald Trump’s top foreign policy priorities stand at pivotal moments as two high-level national security officials head to an annual security forum in Germany. Strains in the trans-Atlantic relationship have cast doubt on whether they can count on much help from European leaders in advancing Trump’s agenda.
headline_main: Stormy US-Europe Relations as Top Officials Head to Munich
headline_print_headline: Stormy US-Europe Relations as Top Officials Head to Munich
